# Environment variables for the PaperLens frontend (new_ui)
#
# When deploying to GitHub Pages, the frontend works fully offline in "Demo Mode"
# (pre-loaded paper, concept map, tooltips). Chat and Manim animations need a
# backend. Set VITE_API_BASE_URL to your deployed backend (e.g. Render) to enable them.
#
# Example (do NOT commit your real key):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://paperlens-backend.onrender.com/api/v1
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
